{"tid":570030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每次射完精 我都會講唔該","createTime":"2018-02-23T09:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T13:03:37.000Z","uid":99227,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b71fe752f1a504cd1694b606a912ff0d2c623b61","tid":570030,"uid":99227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"肥大的身軀壓著我<br />\n身上的老婦不斷鳩un<br />\n【啊啊啊啊 我要射啦】我大聲叫道<br />\n孤獨找到了錯誤的出口 黃精流入巢皮陰道<br />\n激情過後 便是平靜<br />\n我輕輕推開掛在身上的老婦<br />\n她亦十分配合地坐直身子<br />\n難道我是氣功大師嗎<br />\n剛才快要被我操死半生不活的樣子<br />\n在我射精後輕輕一推就龍精虎猛<br />\n【唔該曬 今次真喺辛苦你了】<br />\n我擺低350<br />\n迅速離開"},{"pid":"2bda17a96cb5467dd7c1d26c8ea25c419f597da1","tid":570030,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"350都屌 清睇黎好緊火"},{"pid":"fd7943388af1a13b2b38c4132faf30ddd373b699","tid":570030,"uid":99227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bda17a96cb5467dd7c1d26c8ea25c419f597da1","tid":570030,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"350都屌 清睇黎好緊火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"無辦法<br />\n我屌既喺佢地個經驗<br />\nd老女人收得平<br />\n其實我覺得每一個行業都好<br />\n應該越老越值錢<br />\n佢地既巢皮西<br />\n後生女比唔到我"},{"pid":"6c4aefe26d64096e74787ccadc777c7aed2071d4","tid":570030,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"-.-"},{"pid":"fd67311fb94711d265e9881783f440eefc0cf03e","tid":570030,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b6b609719f08e72f33b9f0bd69ff451616d384e","tid":570030,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6db854c0e56015bfe73d793983c315afee759bc4","tid":570030,"uid":99227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd67311fb94711d265e9881783f440eefc0cf03e","tid":570030,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi